description:
On Today's Episode of the DP show, Dan recaps the historical performance by Tyler Herro in last night Heat/Celtics Game. We're joined by Heat Television Host Jason Jackson and TNT/CBS's Kevin Harlan. Plus, We play the Kevin Harlan Game, can you tell the difference between Harlan and Fritzy's voices?
